│  └────────────────────────────────────────────────┘            │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

### Module Interaction Map

| From → To | Interaction | Data Exchanged |
|-----------|------------|----------------|
| Attention Oracle → Energy Pool | Score submission | Agent ID, Attention Score, timestamp |
| Energy Pool → Reproduction Engine | Energy balance query | Agent ID, VRDE balance |
| Reproduction Engine → Agent Registry | DNA read + Bud mint | Parent DNA, Bud DNA, lineage pointers |
| Agent Registry → Attention Oracle | Agent status check | Agent ID, active/pruned status |
| Governance → All modules | Parameter updates | Parameter name, new value, execution delay |

