## Deployment Architecture

### GitHub Pages Deployment

```
┌──────────────┐     push      ┌──────────────┐     build     ┌──────────────┐
│  Local dev    │ ────────────► │   GitHub      │ ────────────► │  GitHub      │
│              │               │   Repository  │               │  Pages CDN   │
│  index.html  │               │   main branch │               │              │
│  CNAME       │               │               │               │  verdbud.tech│
└──────────────┘               └──────────────┘               └──────────────┘

Flow:
  1. Developer pushes to main branch
  2. GitHub Pages detects change
  3. Static files served from CDN
  4. CNAME routes verdbud.tech to Pages
  5. HTTPS certificate auto-managed by GitHub

No build step required — index.html is served as-is.
```

